originalText.text:
I am INCREDIBLY disappointed in the care, or lack there of, provided by Jeffrey Newmark. I've been ordering the same contacts prescribed by him for 4 years now and I noticed it was time for stronger prescription so months ago I made an appointment through my  PCP to be seen somewhere else. Unfortunately there has been a wait time of about 3 months.
I placed my online order last week for one more month of contacts(with the old prescription) before I will be seen and Jeffrey REFUSES to okay the order. I called him and explained I am almost completely out of contacts and that I am a professional dancer. I can not dance with my glasses, and if I can't dance, I can't make money. I also told him I have an appointment in THREE WEEKS that I'v been waiting for and he still refused. I told him I tried setting up an appointment at another place and it was going to cost me over $200 because very few places accept my specific .
Apparently it's okay for me to wear an outdated prescription for FOUR YEARS, but not one more month later because, how irresponsible?!

originalText.text: Had a phenomenal experience with Dr. Jeffrey Newmark. He was professional, kind and had a great sense of humor. Great priced frames and overall excellent customer service. Thank you for a wonderful experience.
